Module kivakit.core.resource

Package com.telenav.kivakit.core.resource

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ReadableResource
    Interface to an object that is Readable and can be read with a ResourceReader.
    Resource
    A resource that can be read via ReadableResource.
    ResourceFolder
    A resource container is an abstraction that provides access to hierarchical resources, independent of implementation.
    Resourceful
    An object which has a Resource
    WritableResource
    Adds the ability to write to Resource and Writable.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Resource.Converter
    Converts to and from Resources by resolving ResourceIdentifiers.
    ResourceFolder.Converter
    Converts to and from ResourceFolders by resolving strings via ResourceFolderIdentifiers.
    ResourceFolderIdentifier
    An identifier for a ResourceFolder implementation, including either a Package or a Folder.
    ResourceIdentifier
    An arbitrary string that identifies a resource.
    ResourceList
    A list of Resources.
    ResourceList.Converter
    Converts lists of resource identifiers to and from ResourceLists
    ResourcePath
    A path to a resource of any kind.
    ResourcePath.Converter
    Converts to and from ResourcePaths
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    CopyMode
    The mode for copying resources.
